// Template for local signing. Copy this to `DeveloperSettings.xcconfig` (gitignored) and set your
// own Apple Developer Team ID to build/sign on a device. Without it, device builds fail with
// "Signing requires a development team" — simulator/Android builds don't need it.
//
//   cp Darwin/DeveloperSettings.xcconfig.example Darwin/DeveloperSettings.xcconfig
//   # then edit the line below
//
// Find your Team ID in Xcode → Settings → Accounts, or https://developer.apple.com/account (Membership).
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOUR_TEAM_ID
